Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你召唤的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你打破的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不！不要！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服从我然后我会解决你的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开你自己！成为我愿望的一部分！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.16,0:01:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场雪从昨晚一直下到中午
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...接下来这几天天气会变得不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于关西地区的积雪，旅行被打乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好，这里是朝仓住宅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我，你最近好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这很突然，但是希望你能在假期来到这里么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？这真的有点突然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从我到这里做神社巫女的修行我就很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这一个朋友也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很想和你说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有计划...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在和云御西寺庙主持的儿子约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？你怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是巫女，不记得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以带上你男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会来的无论你是否邀请他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过我是巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩内心被邪恶和仇恨占据了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂了么？你需要净化它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你姐妹，所以我不能忽视这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要净化，所以我要请你来大山里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧，但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你保证我会去火车站接你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂？喂？深雪？喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好，深雪...引诱他们去大山里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？我还不知道你有那样的亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是神社巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的预言总是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不愿相信妖兽还跟着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊...那也是我担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒佛变回正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须悼念一下维护寺庙的支持者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？这是云御西寺庙的诅咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:05:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起宗人！我弄疼你了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事，佳代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被诅咒了！爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被诅咒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么削弱了佛像的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我驱逐不了它！你到底再说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人，你承担了1100年前的因果报应...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...在云御西家族的灵魂深处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这么多过时的话干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒佛大人...弥勒佛大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迷失在尘世的痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈，只有你能拯救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Naumaku Samanda Amidaunken Sowaka！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Naumaku Samanda Amidaunken Sowaka！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Naumaku Samanda Amidaunken Sowaka！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人！去大山里！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒佛大人永远不会原谅你，除非你结束你的因果报应！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去山里...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪...这就和深雪说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:07:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊，所以我们必须净化妖兽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和你在一起我敢面对任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我训练的山里没有女人...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未知的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样，我该怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未知区域外面深雪会净化你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪么...？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫女的血液里有神圣的力量...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...将能保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我回来你会很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是感觉...有些担心...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾祸向西方移动了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要超站么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好，很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？你看起来不一样了，性感了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说，真是命运啊，我们能聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...就像你预言的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是宗人 云御西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好，你好，这里，嗯，一点也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪...我们之前在哪遇见过么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了，时间到了！不要和我男朋友搭讪好么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪...我感觉像从哪见过他...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚不要紧张，我们明天早上才去山里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像从前！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我认为女人不会被允许上山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就到门口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有一个让女人净化自己的瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人，快一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能打败被诅咒的命运么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你搓后背，宗人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去给你拿从她小时候的相册了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真的以她的方式帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚在深雪的房间睡，所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，宗人，还没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了么，佳代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了，要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代，我要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒，我爱你，佳代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你，宗人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,, 哦，你好小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，宗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗近...这个时候你想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见不详的云去西面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来看看是否你是对的，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的邪说作为从云御西寺庙驱逐的领导者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次认为我不应该插手，然而..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还愿的雕像被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确信你知道这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云御西家，佛像忠实的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经他犯了一个严重的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在过去他折磨我们很多人，不只是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没想过这回影响宗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按目前状况来看，我们冒险切断...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅是弥勒佛的恩惠，还有从所有神得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送他去了主庙做他的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？去山里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么这么不高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可能是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？寺庙可是圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道寺庙的本质，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山里可是神圣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...但是哪里有邪恶的力量等待复生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...然后颠覆地球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会说...妖兽？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山里跟妖兽的领域是相隔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大山是个独立的世界，跟人心深处是相隔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:18:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen，我的爱人，已经过了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1000年了我一直渴望着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最后我又见到你了，我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？为什么你要从我身边逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有女人可以进到神圣的大山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我会带在这里直到降下神的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我和你成为夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个神的仆人不会因为色欲而玷污他的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我皮肤上留下伤痕你很高兴么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话就结束我的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我，然后跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我，我将只能继续跟着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住我...像这样抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪和我在前世相遇过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不在！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！你在哪？佳代！佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪，等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很奇怪，深雪，发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为什么不告诉宗人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen的气味...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么...？不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1000年的渴望终于要解脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪，你是什么...？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须把你供奉给妖兽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的！为什么！？为什么这样！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代...你将为妖兽王国降低大山的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当这个神圣的地方禁止女人破坏....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...妖兽将会复生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪,你不知道世界会变的多糟糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当妖兽苏醒...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我1000年前的渴望将会被满足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪，你做到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大山和圣地的边界被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人...救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我复活了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代，你的温暖打破了结界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，不要这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我复活的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是天堂！我不能思考了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哥哥和宗人的因果报应么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪的深处...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖兽用了1000年前的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别死了，我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须消除1000年前云御西家的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.53,0:23:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的固执和邪恶的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七大试验变成七大祝福！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.58,0:23:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Naumaku Samanda Basaradan Senta Makarosha Dasabadaya
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的固执和邪恶的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七大试验变成七大祝福！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Naumaku Samanda Basaradan Senta Makarosha Dasabadaya
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Om A Mirj Tatei Zekara Un!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.23,0:24:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.59,0:24:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天堂！天堂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.59,0:24:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Munetara大人，快一点，我等不了了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.60,0:24:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.23,0:24:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.52,0:24:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的技巧真好啊，大祭司！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.27,0:24:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，地狱和天堂有一点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.65,0:24:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个存在中发现真是极喜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.61,0:24:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.90,0:24:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你仅仅是漂浮在山中1000年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.33,0:24:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对妖兽来说是个好盟友...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.87,0:25:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超出了这个界限的祭祀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.29,0:25:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极乐！极乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.96,0:25:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多！更多！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.63,0:25:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.92,0:25:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.64,0:25:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈... 妈妈还没来么！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.10,0:25:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要摆脱妖兽王国束缚的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.44,0:25:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈，只有你能提供这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.00,0:25:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下，你在这附近看见过两个女孩儿么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.96,0:25:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能？\n大山里是禁止女人进入的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.21,0:25:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.34,0:25:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个好的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.97,0:25:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山里时间和空间已经崩坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.89,0:26:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他门两个怎么能发现？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.96,0:26:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Munechika叔叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.05,0:26:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人，佳代在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.05,0:26:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她....
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.39,0:26:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须带她离开这个结界
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.72,0:26:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她破坏了了大山神圣的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.68,0:26:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是佳代和深雪，一个我前世相遇的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.06,0:26:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为只有我哥哥一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.40,0:26:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他儿子前世也充满欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.40,0:27:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔！告诉我！我爸爸怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.41,0:27:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在前世的环境中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.16,0:27:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且帮助妖兽破坏大山色域的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.92,0:27:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.75,0:27:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因果报应
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.09,0:27:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你，他的儿子，不知道他过去罪孽的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.09,0:27:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至他自己也不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.43,0:27:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.43,0:27:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开现实他变成妖兽的仆人了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.43,0:27:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...他是大山的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.39,0:27:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了他1000年前色欲的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.10,0:27:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.77,0:27:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着它，你必须继承他的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.44,0:27:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种...我做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.11,0:27:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将会强奸佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.74,0:27:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这令人毛骨悚然的力量滋养着妖兽
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.08,0:27:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...对圣洁女孩的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.37,0:27:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会让他打破这个地方的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.46,0:27:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.38,0:27:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.47,0:28:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人！你想让我给你更多！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.47,0:28:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈，回答我！为什么隐藏你真实的感受？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.82,0:28:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.53,0:28:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的感觉和妖兽领域...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.53,0:28:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混合在你身体里！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.50,0:28:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭祀，两个洞向你打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.50,0:28:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，就像蠕动的虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.55,0:28:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔！停下！求你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.47,0:28:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.52,0:28:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔...！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.53,0:29:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.54,0:29:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.17,0:29:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么选是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.21,0:29:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.88,0:29:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您爸爸还是你爱人？现在选择吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.19,0:29:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！你是属于妖兽的！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.57,0:29:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开你的腿！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.57,0:29:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪...住手...这不该发生...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.91,0:29:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对，你生来就偷走了宗人的...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.91,0:29:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷走了Sohnen的心
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.25,0:30:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.92,0:30:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.88,0:30:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.26,0:30:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.26,0:30:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪,住手吧，不想杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.60,0:30:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen,我的爱人，我会让你想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.60,0:30:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个温暖我的身体能感受到你！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.27,0:30:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！我不是Sohnen！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.28,0:30:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一千年前就死了并且作为宗人云御西重生了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.28,0:30:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧，Sohnen！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.99,0:30:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪，这是..？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.25,0:30:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经追求你1000年了，我现在不想失去你！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.63,0:30:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好温暖，不是么？来吧，进到我身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.30,0:30:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧我，抱紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.64,0:30:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.64,0:30:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手，如果你不住手的话...！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.27,0:31:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔我！在我的深出...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.98,0:31:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.65,0:31:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.32,0:31:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.66,0:31:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.70,0:31:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开结界！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.66,0:31:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你进到这里的时候大山的神圣就被破坏了..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.62,0:31:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不可能赢的！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.33,0:31:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,征服的时候到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.96,0:31:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候该复仇了，我将再次来到地球上！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.70,0:31:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen，我的爱人！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.04,0:31:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他追上我们了！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.38,0:32:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代，坚持住！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.72,0:32:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen，等等我！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.77,0:32:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.74,0:32:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.28,0:32:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen，我的爱人我不会让你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.58,0:32:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.75,0:32:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.25,0:32:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把他想象成宗人，他已经变成Sohnen Ungyosai了...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.96,0:32:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持续了1000年的因果报应
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.26,0:32:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.30,0:32:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他不在这里解决这个报应，他俩将永远变成一个人！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.43,0:32:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.77,0:33:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪，变回原来的样子吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.27,0:33:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被1000年前的色欲影响了..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.03,0:33:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被妖兽解开的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.11,0:33:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen，你为什么这么说？你为什么还拒绝我？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.45,0:33:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.75,0:33:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我在一起，就一次
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.42,0:33:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我错了，是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.80,0:33:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.84,0:33:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen大人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.13,0:33:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen大人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.30,0:33:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.14,0:33:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen大人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.89,0:34:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.37,0:34:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen大人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.51,0:34:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen大人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.20,0:35:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen大人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.53,0:35:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen大人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.79,0:35:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的遗憾终于没了...哦，多么美好的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.86,0:35:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的东西！他打破结界了！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.28,0:35:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶啊...！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.91,0:36:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.95,0:36:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪，我做到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.29,0:36:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在杀了那个男的在我降到上山之前
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.04,0:36:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后来到我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.63,0:36:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.26,0:36:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.30,0:36:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，不要，我做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.31,0:36:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到你了，妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.02,0:36:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.64,0:36:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.06,0:36:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来我身边吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.61,0:36:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.99,0:36:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪！你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.99,0:36:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点跑，佳代，快点跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.33,0:36:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账！你胆敢反抗我！？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.38,0:36:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.59,0:36:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人，你爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.63,0:37:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.18,0:37:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！你已经堕落到地狱了！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.31,0:37:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.37,0:37:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.62,0:37:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人，快跑吧，我来阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.00,0:37:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山顶的守护神有个标志
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.38,0:37:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是结界外，你能保护佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.05,0:37:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点！但是叔叔...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.05,0:37:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会没事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.59,0:37:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代我们走！\n嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.72,0:37:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！你不能离开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.06,0:37:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.35,0:37:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真行啊，和尚!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.07,0:38:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.41,0:38:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.75,0:38:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.09,0:38:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道我叔叔是否还好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.43,0:38:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.10,0:38:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,, 你是不会逃离我的，妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.78,0:38:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.07,0:38:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人！佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.79,0:38:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,, 放开我，放开我你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.79,0:39:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪！不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.96,0:39:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.30,0:39:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.34,0:39:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sohnen大人，不，宗人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.76,0:39:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你回应我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.48,0:39:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.11,0:39:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.15,0:39:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让你走的，但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.82,0:39:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我重生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.82,0:39:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会再次在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.49,0:39:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.50,0:39:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.52,0:39:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.70,0:40:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里做什么...？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.05,0:40:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代...佳代！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.22,0:40:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.55,0:40:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳代...我们做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.89,0:40:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.22,0:40:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们平时也这么亲热么？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.23,0:40:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.31,0:40:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.23,0:40:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪，你受伤了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.48,0:40:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不，事实上，我感觉很好呦！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.90,0:40:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
